%% Three ways to ship a new version; pick by rollback speed vs cost vs risk control
flowchart TD
    subgraph Rolling [Rolling - zero downtime, slow rollback]
      r1[v1 pods] --> r2[mixed v1/v2] --> r3[v2 pods]
    end
    subgraph BlueGreen [Blue-Green - instant rollback, 2x resources]
      b1[Blue v1 live] --> b2[Green v2 ready] --> b3[flip traffic to Green]
    end
    subgraph Canary [Canary - best risk control, needs observability]
      c1[100% v1] --> c2[5% v2 / 95% v1] --> c3[ramp to 100% v2]
    end
